        "description": "The Circle is a sci-fi/drama narrative experience with interactive elements.  \n\nThe story takes you to a future where \"The Board of the People\" has achieved gender equality by removing our physical capacity to have children. But can they also remove our maternal instincts? \n\nFive women become involved in an illegal situation under the eyes of \"The Board\" when one of them decides to steal and save a sick in-vitro baby from the \"System\", whom otherwise would have been \"repurposed\" (aka killed) for having an incurable disease. \n\nTo heal this baby, they unearth an ancient Greek ritual called the \"Eleusinian Mysteries\", which are said to open a passage into the circle of life and death. \n\nDo you dare to join them in the ritual as the protagonist of the circle?",
